			<div class="post-text">
				<p>Has anyone succeeded in getting a flash file to execute inside of (any) WYSIWYG in-browser editor?</p>
<p>It doesn&#8217;t work for me and I can think of at least one reason why it shouldn&#8217;t (security leak), but has anyone done it anyway?</p>
